  "title": "Xtra Citrusy Norwegian Chorizo Skewers",
  "description": "A low-carb and citrusy Norwegian dish featuring chorizo, yuzu-cure, and pillowy texture, perfect for a dinner meal.",
  "cuisine": "Norwegian",
