      "name": "fresh parsley",
      "amount": "1/4 cup",
      "notes": "chopped"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together yuzu juice, olive oil, lemon zest, garlic, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the sliced chorizo to the bowl and toss to coat with the yuzu mixture.",
    "Thread the chorizo pieces onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "Grill the skewers for 10-12 minutes, turning occasionally, until the chorizo is cooked through.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley and serve immediately."
  ],
